Initial file is THE160ASP160Face001.gro which is created from experimental structure. This file is used to prepare the system for all simulations and the foloowing procedure is followed to prepare the system.

1.  Energy minimization: Steepest descent minimization was performed using the file gromacs-energy-minimization.mdp.

2.  NVT equilibration: The system was equilibrated for 750 ps using a 2 fs time step at a target temperature of 298 K using the file gromacs-nvt-equilibration-md-parameters-base.mdp.

3.  NPT equilibration: Anisotropic Parrinello–Rahman pressure coupling at 1 bar was applied through three consecutive runs of 100 ns (0.1 fs), 3.5 ns (0.2 fs), and 2.5 ns (0.4 fs) time steps. The file named gromacs-npt-md-parameters-base.mdp can be modified to run these simulations.

4.  NPT production: A 25 ns production run was performed under NPT conditions at 1 bar using the Parrinello–Rahman barostat with a 0.2 fs time step
